---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Margdarshak Shikshan Sansthan" description="Learn about Margdarshak Shikshan Sansthan's mission, vision, learning approach, and how we deliver pocket-friendly education with a 100% refund policy.">
  
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="hero-gradient text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 text-center space-y-4">
      <div class="inline-block bg-white/10 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
        Our Foundations
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-headline font-black">
        About Our Institute
      </h1>
      <p class="text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base md:text-lg">
        Providing pocket-friendly, job-oriented education to empower the youth of Bharat.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Institute Intro Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-headline font-bold text-primary">
            Darbhanga's Premier Practical Training Center
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-base">
            Margdarshak Shikshan Sansthan was founded with a singular, powerful objective: **to make high-quality professional training accessible to every single student in Bharat, regardless of their financial background**. 
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-base">
            Located in Benta Chowk, Darbhanga, we are specialized in delivering skill-driven courses in computerized accounting (TallyPrime), tax systems (GST and Income Tax), frontend web coding, and office administration. By emphasizing real client files, practical projects, and a unique 100% attendance fee refund model, we ensure that dedicated learners get certified and employed.
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-6">
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-center">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-[#d9383a]">volunteer_activism</span>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm italic">
                "We believe that education is not a business. Sincerity and hard work should be the only requirements for a student to succeed."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 w-full">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl blur-xl"></div>
            <img alt="Students collaborating" class="relative z-10 rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-[360px] object-cover" src="/assets/ef416198aade12024c457f8fe0004783.png" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-background border-y border-slate-200/50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      
      <!-- Mission Card -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200/60 shadow-lg space-y-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-secondary/10 text-secondary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl font-bold">rocket</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold text-primary">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
            Our mission is to establish a transparent, job-ready ecosystem of technical and vocational learning that matches international standards but remains completely affordable. We aim to equip 10,000+ local students in Bihar with verified modern skills, ensuring that every house has a certified professional capable of driving digital and financial operations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-secondary tracking-widest uppercase">
          Empowering Bharat
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Vision Card -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200/60 shadow-lg space-y-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl font-bold">visibility</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold text-primary">Our Vision</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
            We envision an educational landscape where financial constraints never stand in the way of learning. By expanding our digital portals and modern offline laboratories, we seek to become India’s most trusted student-first institute, establishing a benchmark where professional certification programs are fully subsidized for sincere and hardworking students.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-primary tracking-widest uppercase">
          Building the Future
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Learning Approach & Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 space-y-16">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-3">
        <span class="bg-accent/20 text-[#002D62] px-3.5 py-1 rounded-full font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">
          Our Framework
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-headline font-bold text-primary">
          Our Modern Learning Approach
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm md:text-base">
          How we ensure that our students stand out in interviews and client projects.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <!-- Hybrid Learning -->
        <div class="space-y-4 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-[#d9383a]">devices</span>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-primary">Hybrid Learning Flexibility</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Attend live interactive online lectures or step into our high-speed offline labs at Benta Chowk. We offer complete freedom to switch formats based on your schedule.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Practical Training -->
        <div class="space-y-4 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-[#d9383a]">psychology</span>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-primary">Practical-First Training</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We bypass outdated text files. Our students practice on live databases, write actual web pages, draft official tax documents, and manage commercial ledgers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Certification & Career support -->
        <div class="space-y-4 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-[#d9383a]">verified_user</span>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-primary">Certification & Job Portals</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Upon successful project approvals, earn a government-recognized certificate. We provide placement assistance and share resumes directly with regional corporations.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Why Choose Us Banner CTA -->
      <div class="bg-primary rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-headline font-bold">Ready to Start Your Professional Journey?</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm max-w-xl">
            Choose from our job-oriented courses. Maintain 90% attendance to study for free!
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/register" class="bg-secondary text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-[#c12f31] transition-all shrink-0 shadow-lg hover:scale-105">
          Register for a Course
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
